{"tid":1987459,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［真心問］外國撚有香港身分證但冇香港地址，可以點登記做選民？","createTime":"2020-04-24T13:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T13:13:13.000Z","uid":273294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"896487ea7e788ddc7e2bac9bbb1fe47e321bdbba","tid":1987459,"uid":273294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"226c5ab4e07afdb4ae724bf196fb344dc39e76f9","tid":1987459,"uid":78046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:04:16.000Z","msg":"識唔識人香港住 用佢地址收信"},{"pid":"5bc79a949a6ef5d14295528f0cf90579397666c6","tid":1987459,"uid":221650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:04:34.000Z","msg":"無地址唔可以做選民<br />\n一係搵親戚幫你登記, 不過理論上係要本人住果度, 否則某程度上其實係種票<br />\n不過佢地自己都種唔少啦"},{"pid":"b8d72ceadb916b20fb84734d19f9b800c2ef5a79","tid":1987459,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"問禮義廉，佢哋好熟"},{"pid":"d07f6d350b1168f78412345bc60a477b033b00f3","tid":1987459,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:09:36.000Z","msg":"唔係要通常居港先做得選民咩??"},{"pid":"a3dd62a1c01df08697f2bc5eb13f9b4e7d9deecd","tid":1987459,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:12:17.000Z","msg":"搵禮義廉搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一條龍服務仲有禮品收"},{"pid":"fe75cf49cbbf29bed17222b851c79642be3646e6","tid":1987459,"uid":237947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:13:13.000Z","msg":"要通常在香港居住先符合登記選民條件<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/register-gc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fregister-gc.html&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn%2FulYLG83ImyreQ67A6WOt4%3D&h=ea41d5fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/chi/register-gc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n技術上你可以用通訊地址登記e.g.親戚朋友屋企收信<br />\n但後果自負囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>答十五 : 任何人士如明知或罔顧後果地向選舉事務處提供屬虛假或具誤導性的資料（例如虛假的住址），不論該人有否在選舉中投票，均屬違法。若有關人士其後在選舉中投票，便觸犯由廉政公署負責執行的《選舉（舞弊及非法行為）條例》（第554章）。一經定罪，最高可被判罰款50萬元及監禁7年。<br />\n另外，如選民製造或提供虛假的住址證明意圖使選舉登記主任接受為可接納的住址證明，即屬製造或使用虛假文書的罪行，根據《刑事罪行條例》（第200章）第71條，任何人製造虛假文書，有關行為一經循公訴程序定罪，最高可處監禁14年。 </blockquote>"}]}